pear-pear.horde.org/mnemo.name: pear-pear.horde.org/mnemo
pear-pear.horde.org/mnemo.description: The Mnemo Note Manager is the Horde notes/memos application. It allows users to keep web-based notes and freeform text. Notes may be shared with other users via shared notepads. It requires the Horde Application Framework and an SQL database or Kolab server for backend storage.
